I might be willing to do you this favor.  Bard Charm PL is arguably the fastest in the game.  We go to PC, I pull from the Bandit camp, beat it down to about 5 percent, snare it, charm it (erasing damage record), invis to break charm, snare again, while you beat it down.<br>
